h welcome guest join free  sign in home categories countries my companiess add my company free    share hascol petroleum ltd company descriptionhascol petroleum limited is engaged in the purchase storage and sale of petroleum products such as fuel oil high speed diesel gasoline lpg and lubricants the company was incorporated in  under the  companies ordinance primarily to take advantage of the petroleum sector deregulation and undertake a program for owning leasing and renting oil storage facilities as hascol petroleum ltdll as importing petroleum products for its own account in february  hascol was granted a full marketing license by the government of pakistan and since then hascol has been engaged in developing a retail network under hascol brand and by st december  we will commission over two hundred and fifty retail outlets in the four provinces of pakistan and azad kashmir this number will rise to  by the end of  hascol has developed storage facilities at machike and shikarpur  land has also been acquired at mehmoodkot and daulatpur and storage facilities will be completed by march  at keamari and port qasim hascol has leased tankage under its own management prior to the incorporation of the company the main personnel have been involved in the pakistan oil industry for over thirty years dealing with imports and marketing of refined products such as gas oil fuel oil kerosene gasoline and base oil hascol petroleum limited has independently or through its associated company hascombe limited extensive links with the domestic and international oil trading companies hascol has concluded arrangements with fuchs lubricants of germany to produce and market full range of automotive  industrial lubricants  greases in pakistan hascol is also marketing hascol brand lubricants in the initial stage hascol is getting the lubricants blended under a toll blending agreement and will subsequently put up its own blending and grease plant in karachi hascol is a major supplier of lubricants hascol has started a bunkering division which is supplying high sulphur fuel oil hsfo and marine gas oil mgo at karachi and port qasim hascol has started a bunkering division and will be able to provide bonded supplies of high sulphur fuel oil hsfo and marine gas oil mgo at karachi and port qasim  hascol has also started to market lpg as an automotive fuel through its retail network and for this necessary license has been obtained from ogra and supply arrangements have been made with well known lpg marketing companies in pakistan company informationcontact personmr s ctelephonefaxzipcityislamabadoperational addresssuite  th floor islamabad stock exchange towers blue area islamabad pakistanbusiness typemanufacturer trading company otheryear establishednumber of employees   peopletrade capacity production capacity main productsautomotive lubricantsindustrial lubricantsaddresssuite  th floor ise towers blue arealocationpakistanwebsitevisit website producthpl deo w api cislhpl deo w api cisl pakistan lubricant related companyfaw chemicals suface treatment chemicalsnimexco textile lubricantsglass industry lubricantsspecial lubricantsindustry chemicalssetral …rana agro agri machinerylubricantgahznavee lube oil  stroke engine oilstroke oil gl gear gl oilw super oil …the wholesalers inc textilesbed sheetsfrozen sea foodgeneral itemslubricantfresh vegetablestextilesused …crest engineering  fabricators die lubricantsadmore gas pvt ltd high speed diesel furnace oil motor gasolene kerosene oil light diesel oilpakistan lubricants private ltd diesel engine oil gasoline engine oil  stroke oil gear oil hydraulic oilssimpex corporation chemicalspetrochemicals categoryenergy productspetrochemical productslubricantpakistan energy productspakistan petrochemical productspakistan lubricant related productpolishlubricantsjellyengine oilstopperinjectorfood gradeoil fuelmotor oil countries   china   india   indonesia   malaysia   pakistan   turkey   united kingdom   united states   