e initial stage hascol is getting the lubricants blended under a toll blending agreement and will subsequently put up its own blending and grease plant in karachi hascol is a major supplier of lubricantshascol has started a bunkering division which is supplying high sulphur fuel oil hsfo and marine gas oil mgo at karachi and port qasimhascol has started a bunkering division and will be able to provide bonded supplies of high sulphur fuel oil hsfo and marine gas oil mgo at karachi and port qasim hascol has also started to market lpg as an automotive fuel through its retail network and for this necessary license has been obtained from ogra and supply arrangements have been made with well known lpg marketing companies in pakistan company information countryregion pakistan address suite  th floor ise towers blue area operational address suite  th floor islamabad stock exchange towers blue area islamabad pakistan website httpwwwhascolcom business type manufacturer trading company other main products automotive lubricants industrial lubricants location pakistan year established  number of employess    people trade capacity   production capacity   contact info contact person mr s c telephone fax number zippost code  related product hpl deo w api cisl hpl deo w api cisl pakistan lubricant related company the lubricants company lubricantsfilterscooling towersgas engine spare partsservice contracts total oil pakistan pvt ltd lubricants lubricants lubricator industries lubricator mo tlubricator shahsawarlubricator gear oil  molten sentra pvt ltd oil and gasfuelslubricantsgreasespetro chemicalsoilschemical materialchemical javed brothers shell pakistan chevron pakistan pakistan state oil total atlas castroldelo haroon oils limited industrial oilsautomotive oilsgreases g m supply agencies lubricant ahmed lubricants lubricantsgrease muhammad iqbal khan cementplaster of parisotherslucky cement green agro traders dry red chilliescanola oil seedssunflower oil seedswheatphutti cotton